    <!-- Science attribution -->
    <string name="about_science">About the Science</string>
    <string name="about_science_body">PitchForge\'s training method is drawn from published research on adult absolute pitch acquisition. Studies show that AP is learnable-in-part by most adults with sustained training, and fully learnable by some. For details, see: Wong et al. (2019, 2020, 2025).</string>
